{
  "_comment": [
    "column_order example — demonstrates auto-layout column reordering.",
    "",
    "The 'bus' view has three regions at different addresses.  In SVG,",
    "higher addresses appear at the TOP of the view:",
    "",
    "   TOP    region_c  (0x2000)",
    "          region_b  (0x1000)",
    "   BOTTOM region_a  (0x0000)",
    "",
    "The three detail views are intentionally listed here in the order",
    "A → C → B (scrambled), so without reordering the link bands",
    "would cross.  The auto-layout algorithm sorts column 1 by the",
    "pixel midpoint of each source section, producing the crossing-free",
    "top-to-bottom order:  detail_c → detail_b → detail_a."
  ],
  "views": [
    {
      "id": "bus",
      "title": "Peripheral Bus",
      "sections": [
        { "id": "region_c", "address": "0x2000", "size": "0x1000", "name": "Region C", "min_height": 40 },
        { "id": "region_b", "address": "0x1000", "size": "0x1000", "name": "Region B", "min_height": 40 },
        { "id": "region_a", "address": "0x0000", "size": "0x1000", "name": "Region A", "min_height": 40 }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "detail_a",
      "title": "Region A Detail",
      "_note": "listed 1st in JSON — algorithm moves it to last (bottom) in column",
      "sections": [
        { "id": "a_ctrl", "address": "0x0000", "size": "0x400", "name": "A_CTRL",   "min_height": 30 },
        { "id": "a_stat", "address": "0x0400", "size": "0x400", "name": "A_STATUS", "min_height": 30 },
        { "id": "a_data", "address": "0x0800", "size": "0x800", "name": "A_DATA",   "min_height": 30 }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "detail_c",
      "title": "Region C Detail",
      "_note": "listed 2nd in JSON — algorithm moves it to first (top) in column",
      "sections": [
        { "id": "c_ctrl", "address": "0x2000", "size": "0x400", "name": "C_CTRL",   "min_height": 30 },
        { "id": "c_stat", "address": "0x2400", "size": "0x400", "name": "C_STATUS", "min_height": 30 },
        { "id": "c_data", "address": "0x2800", "size": "0x800", "name": "C_DATA",   "min_height": 30 }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "detail_b",
      "title": "Region B Detail",
      "_note": "listed 3rd in JSON — algorithm moves it to middle in column",
      "sections": [
        { "id": "b_ctrl", "address": "0x1000", "size": "0x400", "name": "B_CTRL",   "min_height": 30 },
        { "id": "b_stat", "address": "0x1400", "size": "0x400", "name": "B_STATUS", "min_height": 30 },
        { "id": "b_data", "address": "0x1800", "size": "0x800", "name": "B_DATA",   "min_height": 30 }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "links": [
    { "from": { "view": "bus", "sections": ["region_c"] }, "to": { "view": "detail_c" } },
    { "from": { "view": "bus", "sections": ["region_b"] }, "to": { "view": "detail_b" } },
    { "from": { "view": "bus", "sections": ["region_a"] }, "to": { "view": "detail_a" } }
  ]
}
